1. Run the compiled executable.
2. Use the arrow keys to navigate through the available modes.
3. Press 'q' to exit the program.


Arrow Key Controls
Up Arrow (↑): Increment the second mode.
Down Arrow (↓): Decrement the second mode.
Left Arrow (←): Increment the first mode.
Right Arrow (→): Decrement the first mode.
Exit Control
'q': Quit the program.
